{"tid":1314577,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"⬤ 「電飯煲之父」蒙民偉骨灰盅離奇出現在金山郊野公園","createTime":"2019-07-14T08:55:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T19:37:14.000Z","uid":35221,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"094d67d38cbb0dd04f3969ac57053763dbe6b6f8","tid":1314577,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T08:55:06.000Z","msg":"「電飯煲之父」蒙民偉  骨灰盅離奇出現在金山郊野公園<br />\n07月14日(日) 16:09<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190714/photo/bkn-20190714160905855-0714_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190714164541\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190714%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190714160905855-0714_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190714164541&h=413b76fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20130119/photo/0119-00412-003b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20130119%2Fphoto%2F0119-00412-003b1.jpg&h=afe6332b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跑馬地黃泥涌道天主教墳場再有名人骨灰盅離奇失竊。今日(14日)下午1時許，警方接獲一名男子報案，指其姓蒙妻子在金山郊野公園擔任清潔工，上周五(12日)在石梨貝水塘2號燒烤場清理垃圾時，在泥土內赫見一個寫有「蒙民偉」的骨灰盅，其妻不知蒙民偉是名人，惟因同姓惦記在心，事後向丈夫分享此事，其夫知悉後大驚，遂報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n警方隨後接報到場，不排除有關骨灰盅在跑馬地天主教墳場失竊，隨後已檢走骨灰盅，並聯絡墳場人員及相關家屬了解事件。根據資料，「電飯煲之父」、信興集團始創人兼慈善家蒙民偉在2010年逝世，安葬在跑馬地天主教墳場。<br />\n<br />\n黃泥涌道天主教墳場早前亦發生名人骨灰盅被盜案，前日(12日)下午1時許，一名姓高(46歲)男子到場拜祭先人時，發現已故女星尤敏與丈夫高福球合葬的骨灰龕位遭破壞，雲石面被扑爛，兩個骨灰盅及一條唸珠被盜去，於是報警。警方接報到場，在附近一帶兜截，惜無發現，案件列盜竊案處理，交由灣仔警區刑事調查隊跟進，並追緝涉案人士歸案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190714/bkn-20190714160905855-0714_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190714%2Fbkn-20190714160905855-0714_00822_001.html&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPahX1SmvCJyfLMOcbfj5ioUM%3D&h=bf0428e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190714/bkn-20190714160905855-0714_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8c36525f7f35f1e891174bc3fc1959ca055db5ed","tid":1314577,"uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T08:55:53.000Z","msg":"早兩日尤敏同佢老公個位先畀人爆完嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n⬤ 已故影星尤敏與丈夫合葬龕位遭破壞，骨灰被盜<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1309523\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1309523</a>"},{"pid":"1f0ea7f1eefaa888775f7da7ad604bf31d46f34c","tid":1314577,"uid":67329,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T08:56:55.000Z","msg":"目的係咩"},{"pid":"e41bd757de671c86864650d6c5f8babc23996b1e","tid":1314577,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f0ea7f1eefaa888775f7da7ad604bf31d46f34c","tid":1314577,"uid":67329,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T08:56:55.000Z","msg":"目的係咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T08:58:10.000Z","msg":"可能真係好似尤敏post有巴打話齋，涉及勒索，蒙民偉同尤敏呢啲都已經係上幾代名人，都係葬跑馬地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb8eda2346f0e9fa796e9df24b7c113ccce898c","tid":1314577,"uid":193642,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T08:58:39.000Z","msg":"香港連死左嘅人都唔安全"},{"pid":"cfa25a94a279b55a6b8758d4956df11114d32712","tid":1314577,"uid":5267,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T08:58:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ab1ab6ae41bdd32e585d442f42c1eac6e7029ec","tid":1314577,"uid":67329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e41bd757de671c86864650d6c5f8babc23996b1e","tid":1314577,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f0ea7f1eefaa888775f7da7ad604bf31d46f34c","tid":1314577,"uid":67329,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T08:56:55.000Z","msg":"目的係咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T08:58:10.000Z","msg":"可能真係好似尤敏post有巴打話齋，涉及勒索，蒙民偉同尤敏呢啲都已經係上幾代名人，都係葬跑馬地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T08:59:34.000Z","msg":"勒索既話點解會隨便掉喺山邊"},{"pid":"492a7fe16eafd20ed06ab0ee9f6015